      category.style.display = 'block';
      } else if (visibleCards.length > 0) {

      category.style.display = 'none';

      document.getElementById('modalMatchCompetition').textContent = report.competition;

      document.getElementById('modalAwayTeam').textContent = report.awayTeam;
      document.getElementById('modalAwayTeamLineup').textContent = report.awayTeam;
      document.getElementById('modalPossession').textContent = report.possession;
      document.getElementById('modalShots').textContent = report.shots;
      document.getElementById('modalCorners').textContent = report.corners;
      document.getElementById('modalHighlights').textContent = report.highlights;
      // Populate home lineup
      const homeLineupDiv = document.getElementById('modalHomeLineup');
      homeLineupDiv.innerHTML = '';

      homeLineupDiv.appendChild(playerDiv);
      });
      // Populate away lineup
      const awayLineupDiv = document.getElementById('modalAwayLineup');
      awayLineupDiv.innerHTML = '';
      report.awayLineup.forEach(player => {
      const playerDiv = document.createElement('div');
      playerDiv.className = 'lineup-player';
      playerDiv.textContent = player;
      awayLineupDiv.appendChild(playerDiv);
      });
      // Show modal
      document.getElementById('matchReportModal').style.display = 'block';
      document.body.style.overflow = 'hidden';
      }
      });

      function closeMatchReport() {
      document.getElementById('matchReportModal').style.display = 'none';
      document.body.style.overflow = 'auto';
      }
      // Checkout functionality
      let currentProduct = null;
      let currentPrice = null;
      let currentCategory = null;
      function openCheckoutModal(productName, price, category) {
      currentProduct = productName;
      currentPrice = price;
      currentCategory = category;
      document.getElementById('checkoutTitle').textContent = Checkout - ${ productName };
      document.getElementById('productName').value = productName;
      document.getElementById('productPrice').value = ${ price } KZT;
      updateTotalPrice();
      document.getElementById('checkoutModal').style.display = 'block';
      document.body.style.overflow = 'hidden';
      }
      function closeCheckoutModal() {
      document.getElementById('checkoutModal').style.display = 'none';
      document.body.style.overflow = 'auto';
      document.getElementById('checkoutForm').reset();
      }
      function updateTotalPrice() {
      const quantity = parseInt(document.getElementById('quantity').value);
      const price = parseInt(currentPrice);
      const total = quantity * price;
      document.getElementById('totalPrice').textContent = ${ total } KZT;
      }
      document.getElementById('quantity').addEventListener('change', updateTotalPrice);
      // Checkout form submission
      document.getElementById('checkoutForm').addEventListener('submit', function (e) {
      e.preventDefault();
      const name = document.getElementById('name').value;
      const email = document.getElementById('email').value;
      const phone = document.getElementById('phone').value;
      const quantity = document.getElementById('quantity').value;
      const payment = document.getElementById('payment').value;
      const orderData = {
      product: currentProduct,
      price: currentPrice,
      category: currentCategory,
      quantity: quantity,
      total: parseInt(currentPrice) * parseInt(quantity),
      customer: {
      name: name,
      email: email,
      phone: phone,
      city: document.getElementById('city').value,
      address: document.getElementById('address').value
      },
      payment: payment
      };
      // In a real application, you would send this data to a server
      console.log('Order submitted:', orderData);
      // Show success message
      alert(Thank you for your order, ${ name }!\n\nOrder Summary: \n${ currentProduct } x${ quantity } \nTotal: ${ orderData.total } KZT\n\nYou will receive a confirmation email at ${ email }.);
      // Close modal
      closeCheckoutModal();
      // In a real app, you would redirect to payment gateway
      if (payment === 'kaspi' || payment === 'halyk') {
      setTimeout(() => {
      alert('Redirecting to payment gateway...');
      // window.location.href = https://payment.ordabasy.kz/checkout?order=${encodeURIComponent(JSON.stringify(orderData))};
      }, 500);
      }
      });
      // Close modals when clicking outside
      window.addEventListener('click', function (event) {
      const matchModal = document.getElementById('matchReportModal');
      const checkoutModal = document.getElementById('checkoutModal');
      if (event.target === matchModal) {
      closeMatchReport();
      }
      if (event.target === checkoutModal) {
      closeCheckoutModal();

      e.preventDefault();
      const targetId = this.getAttribute('href');
      if (targetId === '#') return;
      const targetElement = document.querySelector(targetId);
      if (targetElement) {
      window.scrollTo({
      top: targetElement.offsetTop - 80,
      behavior: 'smooth'
      });
      }
      });

      // Function to toggle sections visibility (for FULL HISTORY, STADIUM TOURS, OUR VALUES)
      function toggleSection(sectionId) {
      const section = document.getElementById(sectionId);
      const button = event.target;
      // If section is visible - hide it, if hidden - show it
      if (section.style.display === 'block') {
      section.style.display = 'none';
      button.classList.remove('active-btn');
      } else {
      // Hide all sections first
      const allSections = document.querySelectorAll('.hidden-section');
      allSections.forEach(sec => {
      sec.style.display = 'none';
      });
      // Remove active class from all buttons
      const allButtons = document.querySelectorAll('#club .btn');
      allButtons.forEach(btn => {
      btn.classList.remove('active-btn');
      });
      // Show selected section and make button active
      section.style.display = 'block';
      button.classList.add('active-btn');
      // Smooth scroll to opened section
      section.scrollIntoView({ behavior: 'smooth', block: 'nearest' });
      }
      }
      // Function to open all sections
      function openAllSections() {
      const allSections = document.querySelectorAll('.hidden-section');
      const allButtons = document.querySelectorAll('#club .btn');
      allSections.forEach(section => {
      section.style.display = 'block';
      });
      allButtons.forEach(button => {
      button.classList.add('active-btn');
      });
      }
      // Function to close all sections
      function closeAllSections() {
      const allSections = document.querySelectorAll('.hidden-section');
      const allButtons = document.querySelectorAll('#club .btn');
      allSections.forEach(section => {
      section.style.display = 'none';
      });
      allButtons.forEach(button => {
      button.classList.remove('active-btn');
      });
      }
